tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_interactions_ar_content (
    interaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    ar_content_id INT NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_interactions_ar_content (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  content_id INT,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_behavior_analysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  time_on_page INT,
  clicks_count INT,
  scroll_depth INT
);

CREATE TABLE UserInteractionsARContent (
    interaction_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    ar_content_id INT NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (interaction_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ARContent (
    ar_content_id INT NOT NULL,
    ar_content_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    ar_content_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    ar_content_description TEXT,
    PRIMARY KEY (ar_content_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Users (
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    user_email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    user_age INT,
    user_gender CHAR(1),
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE BehaviorAnalysis (
    evaluation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    interaction_id UUID,
    activity_id UUID,
    behavior_rating INTEGER
);

CREATE TABLE interaction_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    ar_content_id INT,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    analysis_result VARCHAR(255)
);
